paris 36 ( french : faubourg 36 ) is a 2008 french romantic drama film directed by christophe barratier . this film is set in 1930s paris . the song " loin de paname " ( lyrics by frank thomas , music by reinhardt wagner ) , sung by nora arnezeder , was nominated for the 82nd academy awards for best original song . the film is a co-production of france , germany , and the czech republic .